            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Agencies that want one platform for keywords, competitors, and audits.</div>
            <a href="https://semrush.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">03</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Ahrefs</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best backlink data + competitive analysis</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$129<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Lite plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Largest live backlink index in the category</li>
                <li>Content Explorer for topic and competitor research</li>
                <li>Rank tracking, audit, and Webmaster Tools (free)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Pay-per-credit on some reports</li>
                <li>Multi-user pricing climbs sharply</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Agencies whose retainers include link-building or technical SEO.</div>
            <a href="https://ahrefs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
