            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Agencies whose clients are dominated by local service businesses.</div>
            <a href="https://brightlocal.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
